name: Himchan
dialog: Oh? You came to exercise early this morning.

name: 주인공
dialog: I wanted to exercise with Himchan, so I came early.

name: Himchan
dialog: Hahaha... You know it too! Exercising with two people is more fun than alone.

name: Himchan
dialog: Then let's do an exercise that we can do together today.

name: Himchan
dialog: Right away, badminton! Have you ever played badminton?

name: 주인공
dialog: No, I have seen people play badminton, but I have never played it myself.

name: Himchan
dialog: Great. First, prepare a badminton racket and a shuttlecock shaped like a feather.

name: Himchan
dialog: Hold the racket so that the racket face is parallel to the ground and the racket is standing upright from the ground. Hold the racket handle like a handshake.

name: Himchan
dialog: Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent.

name: Himchan
dialog: Alright, let's get started. Keep your elbow up and the racket standing upright, because you don't know when and where the shuttlecock will fly.

name: Himchan
dialog: Is this your first time playing? Why are you so good at it?

name: Himchan
dialog: Even though I'm a badminton expert, would you like to play a match with me? Haha.
